{"tid":61173,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"我 正式宣布：籃球=玩具","createTime":"2016-12-31T04:35:22.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-31T13:51:22.000Z","uid":63687,"like":8,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b0034df630756f53fcf7a6e232d9884845899318","tid":61173,"uid":63687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T04:35:22.000Z","msg":"一睇籃球機就知佢係整黎畀人玩既玩具啦<br />\n<br />\n而足球就係畀狗玩既玩具<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （youtube keywords: 人狗足球賽）<br />\n守龍又得，用個頭將個波頂入龍又得<br />\n<br />\n籃球真係好撚廢，屌你老母你地話啲狗點拍波點射波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇人知而家舉行到第幾屆？好想現場睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35a4ded44094f0b85ba94962ba27818ef50a5f50","tid":61173,"uid":7824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T04:41:41.000Z","msg":"足球機仲似玩具啦下話"},{"pid":"3feebd462c80ad10834a9d07b4a403951467f0c1","tid":61173,"uid":63687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T05:00:15.000Z","msg":"足球撚你地話我講得岩唔岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3db308a14f1adbdae1b3c5521bf8644c8a6b4734","tid":61173,"uid":35712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T13:51:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/kjrtemul\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fkjrtemul&h=9abfabc8&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}